  "projectDescription": "A full-stack e-learning platform for the Instituto de Economía y Empresa (IEE) built with Laravel 12, Inertia.js, and Vue 3, featuring course management, subscription plans, a virtual classroom, exams, certificates, and an admin dashboard.",
